---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ProjectDetails from "../../../components/ProjectDetails.astro";

import MchTabletView from "./mch-tablet-view.png";
import MchPaymentFlow from "./mch-payment-flow.png";
import MchAppointment from "./mch-appointment.png";
import MchPayment from "./mch-payment.png";
import MchDashboard from "./mch-dashboard-specs.png";
---

<article id="mchanywhere" class="text-sunset bg-linear-(--mch-gradient) section-space">
  <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wide uppercase opacity-60 mb-2">Telemedicine app. iOS, Android, Web.</p>
  <h3 class="section-header">
    <span class="bg-black text-yellow">MCHAnywhere</span> helps patients get
    remote consultations from MCH's doctors.
  </h3>

  <ProjectDetails
    role="UI/UX Design for iOS & Android + Web development (html/css/js)"
    projectDate="2015"
    projName="MCH Anywhere"
  />

  <div class="mx-auto my-16">
    <Image
      src={MchTabletView}
      sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"
      alt="MCH Anywhere telemedicine app on tablet — appointment and consultation screens"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <p class="max-w-sm mt-8 text-md">
    Designed a telemedicine app for Miami Children's Hospital (now Nicklaus) — making remote pediatric consultations simple, fast, and secure.
  </p>
  <figure class="mx-auto my-16">
    <Image
      src={MchPaymentFlow}
      sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"
      alt="MCH Anywhere payment flow — step-by-step booking process for parents"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <figcaption class="fig-caption">Invoice page</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <!-- <h3 class="section-subtitle">Breadboarding</h3>
  <div class="max-w-sm my-6 text-white text-md">
    <p>
      We wired the whole process of cancelling a product from the very concept,
      to each of the steps in detail in order to define each step as needed.
    </p>
  </div> -->
  <div
    class="grid-cols-1 section-spread sm:grid-cols-2 pswp-gallery"
    id="mch-gallery"
  >
    <a
      href={MchAppointment.src}
      data-pswp-width={MchAppointment.width}
      data-pswp-height={MchAppointment.height}
      target="_blank"
    >
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={MchAppointment}
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Appointment"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <figcaption class="fig-caption">Appointments showing all available spots and quick reservation.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
    <a
      href={MchPayment.src}
      data-pswp-width={MchPayment.width}
      data-pswp-height={MchPayment.height}
      target="_blank"
    >
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={MchPayment}
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Payment"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <figcaption class="fig-caption">The copy and icons reinforces the privacy and security standards.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p class="max-w-sm mb-8 text-md">
   The goal was to streamline appointment booking and payment for parents under stress. Clear copy, intuitive flows, and precise developer specs for the iOS/Android team.
  </p>

  <p class="max-w-sm mb-8 text-md">
    The payment process was streamlined for parents to get an appointment quickly and secure.
  </p>
  <figure>
    <Image
      class={"pic-withloader"}
      src={MchDashboard}
      sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"
      alt="MCH Anywhere dashboard with developer specs for iOS and Android implementation"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <figcaption class="fig-caption">Dashboard specs for implementation. Details were crucial for the iOS/Android development team.</figcaption>
  </figure>
</article>
